#for j in trjson [:3]:
for j in trjson:
    j['City']=[]
    j['ISP']=[]
    j['UniqueCities']=[]
    j['UniqueISPs']=[]
    j['UniqueCities_len']=0
    j['UniqueISPs_len']=0
    j['PercentOfUnresolvedCities']=0.0
    j['PercentOfUnresolvedISPs']=0.0
    j['NbrOfBigCDNs']=0
    j['ListOfBigCDNs']=[]
    j['NbrOfBigISPs']=0
    j['ListOfBigISPs']=[]
    uniquecities={}
    uniqueisps={} 
    for h in j['Hops']:
        try:
            j['City'].append(ip_dict[h]['city'])
            j['ISP'].append(ip_dict[h]['isp'])
            if ip_dict[h]['city'] in uniquecities.keys():
                uniquecities[ip_dict[h]['city']]=+1
            else:
                uniquecities[ip_dict[h]['city']]=+1
            if ip_dict[h]['isp'] in uniqueisps.keys():
                uniqueisps[ip_dict[h]['isp']]=+1
            else:
                uniqueisps[ip_dict[h]['isp']]=+1
        except KeyError:
            if h.startswith("192.168") or h.startswith("10.0") or h.startswith("10.1"):
                j['City'].append("Local:"+h)
                j['ISP'].append("Local:"+h)
            else:
                j['City'].append("Unresolved:"+h)
                j['ISP'].append("Unresolved:"+h)
    
    j['UniqueCities']=list(uniquecities.keys())
    j['UniqueISPs']=list(uniqueisps.keys())
    j['UniqueCities_len']=len(uniquecities.keys())
    j['UniqueISPs_len']=len(uniqueisps.keys())
    
    try:
        j['DeviceISP']=di_dict[j['id']]['isp']
    except KeyError:
        j['DeviceISP']="Unknown"
        
    for c in j['City']:
        if c is nan:
            j['PercentOfUnresolvedCities']+=1.0
    j['PercentOfUnresolvedCities'] = j['PercentOfUnresolvedCities'] / len(j['City']) * 100
    for i in j['ISP']:
        if i is nan:
            j['PercentOfUnresolvedISPs']+=1.0
        elif i in listOfBigCDNs:
            j['NbrOfBigCDNs']+=1
            j['ListOfBigCDNs'].append(i)
    for i in j['UniqueISPs']:
        if i not in j['ListOfBigCDNs'] and i is not j['DeviceISP']:
            j['NbrOfBigISPs']+=1
            j['ListOfBigISPs'].append(i)
        
    j['PercentOfUnresolvedISPs'] = j['PercentOfUnresolvedISPs'] / len(j['ISP']) * 100
    try:
        j['DestHostLocation']=ip_dict[j['DestHost']]['city']
    except KeyError:
        j['DestHostLocation']="Unknown"
    try:
        j['DestHostISP']=ip_dict[j['DestHost']]['isp']
    except KeyError:
        j['DestHostISP']="Unknown"
    try:
        j['DeviceLocation']=di_dict[j['id']]['city_x']
    except KeyError:
        j['DeviceLocation']="Unknown"
    try:
        j['DeviceLocationY']=di_dict[j['id']]['city_y']
    except KeyError:
        j['DeviceLocationY']="Unknown"
